sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant CI as GitHub Actions
  participant Repo as cicd-gitops-pipeline<br/>(this repo)
  participant Argo as ArgoCD
  participant K8s as RKE2 API server
  participant Pod as workload pod

  CI->>Repo: commit (kustomize edit set image)
  Note over Argo: poll loop ~3 min<br/>+ webhook on push

  Argo->>Repo: git fetch + kustomize build
  Argo->>K8s: server-side apply (Deployment, Service, Ingress)
  K8s-->>Argo: applied with new ReplicaSet
  K8s->>Pod: create new pods<br/>(image pulled from GHCR)
  Pod-->>K8s: Ready=true
  K8s->>Pod: terminate old ReplicaSet pods
  Argo->>Repo: status: Synced + Healthy

  Note over Argo,K8s: selfHeal: true<br/>any out-of-band kubectl edit<br/>is reverted within minutes
